    "difficulty": 1,
    "question": "下列代数式中，哪些是整式？\n(1) 3x² + 2x + 1\n(2) 4/(x+1)\n(3) √x\n(4) 5y³ - 7y + 9",
    "options": [
      "A. (1)和(4)",
